parasitic vision
Discworld ritual help
parasitic vision

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Parasitic vision - Taps a spiritually linked victim to share their vision.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Parasitic vision is an offensive ritual, which can be used to see through another's eyes, seeing what they see.  You may only perform this ritual if you have some sort of spiritual dominance over another.  To perform this ritual you will need a holy symbol of your god.
.EP
